Bharathi Azhaghu Tamil Unicode fonts  published by Bharathi
Puthakaalayam in collaboration with ChalkPiece Foundation
under CC-By-SA-4.0 license. This is the collection of
808 fonts and about 2102 font typefaces. 
The catalogue of fonts is in the doc folder.

This package contains the two star fonts
totaling 652 font typefaces for official and proffessional usage.


